{"tid":2225629,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新世界擬售產150億  秉持「現金為王」否認撤資","createTime":"2020-10-01T12:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T00:45:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4fdfb0b4efaace608abb9bb7e500c76e93bf738d","tid":2225629,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201001/U4R4SN2JKZBENFLDSHEYFY5BNY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201001%2FU4R4SN2JKZBENFLDSHEYFY5BNY%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1zY9GQwUZQLLS4G4eGYLUm4%3D&h=672a42e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201001%2FU4R4SN2JKZBENFLDSHEYFY5BNY%2F&h=d732bd98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201001/U4R4SN2JKZBENFLDSHEYFY5BNY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n新世界擬售產150億 <br />\n秉持「現金為王」否認撤資<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_qN6ASAxvObveAcvcWpBwGfN8Dg=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QDIESPZWBD6PL5HNCJBLS5JDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_qN6ASAxvObveAcvcWpBwGfN8Dg%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5QDIESPZWBD6PL5HNCJBLS5JDQ.jpg&h=a7570382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄭志剛指K11 MUSEA於疫市中表現強勁。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社會運動加上疫情衝擊，新世界（017）至今年6月全年收入跌23%，股東應佔溢利暴跌94%。執行副主席兼總經理鄭志剛指，會秉持「現金為王」策略，並計劃出售非核心資產，或涉資150億元，集團現有逾千億資金覓機會趁低吸納。他又否認賣走資產是要從香港撤資，「集團今年成立50周年，對香港富有感情。」目前新世界無裁員計劃。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大圍站上蓋最細278呎<br />\n<br />\n新世界公佈去年全年業績，集團期內收入減少23%至590億元，其中物業發展收入減50%至192.1億元，主要來自香港傲瀧、名鑄、迎海系列等住宅項目，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現有逾千億資金覓投資<br />\n<br />\n鄭志剛指集團採取「現金為王」的策略，去年已出售約106億元非核心資產，據資料當中包括上環信德中心內部份物業、德福廣場二期商場及PopCorn 2商場等。今年新世界會加碼出售130至150億元非核心資產。鄭志剛於今年2月提及，有意出售只持少數股份或未管握控制權的項目。他補充，「集團可動用資金達千億，期望於疫市中能趁低吸納，部署更有價值的投資。」<br />\n<br />\n他強調出售資產並非撤資，根據資料新世界資金在疫情下轉入內地，今年8月以41億人民幣投得上海黃浦區淮海中路地皮。鄭。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n新世界持續重整業務，光大新鴻基財富管理策略師溫傑表示，集團出售非核心資產，的確可令其估值折讓收窄，利好股價。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新創建少賺94% 派29仙<br />\n<br />\n同系新創建（659）亦公佈全年業績，股東應佔溢利跌94%至2.53億元，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FLiJ8-DJVzOLXO4F3_7PBKhFV18=/659x384/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PWIXKEWOYNHTXK63A7BVP3BCAU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFLiJ8-DJVzOLXO4F3_7PBKhFV18%3D%2F659x384%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPWIXKEWOYNHTXK63A7BVP3BCAU.gif&h=1b7ac5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wEY2FpeXoxj13UP4VgtWy2i2M9g=/539x384/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NQJYJ6NUGZHMJES6EUXDQW7X4Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwEY2FpeXoxj13UP4VgtWy2i2M9g%3D%2F539x384%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNQJYJ6NUGZHMJES6EUXDQW7X4Y.gif&h=dc7de7cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c2b18ad50ebc7b35ba773b78c47f184c46de632","tid":2225629,"uid":53577,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"新世界新鴻基呢d叫九世乞衣種, 乞衣永遠都係乞衣, 叫佢食屎就食屎,含撚就含撚, 有多多錢都改變唔到宿命."},{"pid":"4bcf202fb6c05918a2076622a51306d79a5860fe","tid":2225629,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"老千股"},{"pid":"0146603cdcfad222186a59d4f71d3ff7c14e6d9d","tid":2225629,"uid":137694,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c2b18ad50ebc7b35ba773b78c47f184c46de632","tid":2225629,"uid":53577,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:44:42.000Z","msg":"新世界新